							<p>I provide free consultation for all spaces either in person or by email if you choose . All email consultations require photographs of the space to be painted as well as the demensions of the walls. The price you are quoted after your initial consultation will be the final price unless you choose to add more to the mural. There will never be any hidden extra fees. All materials are included in the mural pricing.</p>

